{"tid":2302354,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"產品難維修 亞馬遜蘋果「海嘯式浪費」","createTime":"2020-11-27T05:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T02:06:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c071bbf7935766a9f4990b0e9c957cab94a34577","tid":2302354,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:13:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201127/MK74PZUUCNEX5A7FP33QFEANDM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201127%2FMK74PZUUCNEX5A7FP33QFEANDM%2F&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=2dd91e7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201127%2FMK74PZUUCNEX5A7FP33QFEANDM%2F&h=290119b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201127/MK74PZUUCNEX5A7FP33QFEANDM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n產品難維修 亞馬遜蘋果「海嘯式浪費」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/plmuHgQgdZbz5AO0BKe3EnbfXow=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QILBC3N4MJBJDDSTWOTR25IGPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FplmuHgQgdZbz5AO0BKe3EnbfXow%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQILBC3N4MJBJDDSTWOTR25IGPA.jpg&h=5dfaeae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蘋果被斥間接製造海量電子垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英議員倡「維修權」<br />\n<br />\n議員指政府應把「維修權」列入法例，使消費者更易獲得維修說明書、可負擔的替換零件，和確保維修不會因缺乏特定工具而無法進行；又建議削減維修服務的增值稅。議員又指政府應禁止企業刻意縮短產品的壽命，所有電子產品應貼上標籤，註明預期壽命、可接受軟件更新的時期，以及「可維修度得分」。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》"},{"pid":"f9b60d947baa00feab05d094cd411fc58b3ff3d8","tid":2302354,"uid":345516,"like":37,"dislike":4,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"蘋果：我地好環保，已經冇送充電頭同耳機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.g